OL,3,CBurnham eyes Westminster return as MP
OL,4,Cstands aside to allow challenge to
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer's leadership was
OL,8,Funder intense pressure as a Labour MP
OL,9,Fstood aside to allow Andy Burnham to
OL,10,Fattempt to return to Parliament and
OL,11,Fchallenge the Prime Minister.
OL,13,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester said
OL,14,Fhe wanted to return to Westminster to
OL,15,F"make politics work properly for
OL,16,Fpeople" after Josh Simons, the Labour
OL,17,FMP for Makerfield, said he would stand
OL,18,Fdown so Mr Burnham can "drive the
OL,19,Fchange our country is crying out for".
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@GO]zD@XOU{D@eO]
