OL,3,CBurnham eyes Westminster return as MP
OL,4,Cstands aside to allow challenge to
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FSources said Sir Keir will not seek to
OL,8,Fblock Mr Burnham from becoming
OL,9,FLabour's candidate in the forthcoming
OL,10,Fby-election, but first the party's
OL,11,FNational Executive Committee needs to
OL,12,Fgive him the green light to stand when
OL,13,Fit meets next week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
