OL,3,CBurnham eyes Westminster return as MP
OL,4,Cstands aside to allow challenge to
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FSir Keir has faced mounting calls to
OL,8,Fquit in the wake of Labour's
OL,9,Fdisastrous local election results last
OL,10,Fweek, prompting speculation his
OL,11,Fcritics within the Cabinet were
OL,12,Fprepared to tell him it was time to
OL,13,Fresign.
OL,15,FBut by lunchtime on Thursday, only Mr
OL,16,FStreeting, who was later replaced by
OL,17,Fformer chief secretary to the Treasury
OL,18,FJames Murray, had quit the Government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
