OL,3,CBurnham eyes Westminster return as MP
OL,4,Cstands aside to allow challenge to
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FHowever, in doing so, he had not ` as
OL,8,Fsome had expected ` launched a
OL,9,Fleadership bid in the process, as he
OL,10,Furged Sir Keir to allow the "best
OL,11,Fpossible field of candidates" to run
OL,12,Fto replace him in Downing Street.
OL,14,FIt is still unclear whether Mr
OL,15,FStreeting has the support of 81 Labour
OL,16,FMPs as needed to launch a formal
OL,17,Fchallenge against the Prime Minister.
OL,26,@rD@]OUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
