OL,3,CBurnham eyes Westminster return as MP
OL,4,Cstands aside to allow challenge to
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FBy mid-afternoon on Thursday, there
OL,8,Fwas still no leadership challenge
OL,9,Funder way and attention turned to Mr
OL,10,FBurnham to see whether he would launch
OL,11,Fhis own challenge.
OL,13,FBut as he announced on social media
OL,14,Fhis plan to return to Westminster, Mr
OL,15,FBurnham hinted any leadership contest
OL,16,Fshould wait until he was an MP.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
