OL,3,CBurnham eyes Westminster return as MP
OL,4,Cstands aside to allow challenge to
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FWhile some 89 MPs have so far publicly
OL,8,Fcalled for Sir Keir's resignation,
OL,9,Fthey are not united behind a single
OL,10,Fcandidate to replace him.
OL,12,FIf he did not step down, Sir Keir
OL,13,Fwould automatically be on the ballot
OL,14,Fpaper in any race, and Downing Street
OL,15,Fhas continued to insist that he would
OL,16,Ffight any effort to oust him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
