OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778803375
OL,3,CBurnham eyes Westminster return as MP
OL,4,Cstands aside to allow challenge to
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FMr Streeting's is the first departure
OL,8,Ffrom the Cabinet, after the
OL,9,Fresignations on Tuesday of junior
OL,10,Fministers Jess Phillips, Zubir Ahmed,
OL,11,FAlex Davies-Jones and Miatta
OL,12,FFahnbulleh.
OL,14,FArmed forces minister Al Carns and
OL,15,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband have also
OL,16,Fbeen tipped as potential leadership
OL,17,Fcandidates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
